i2v-kamui-veo31-fast.description: Google Veo3.1 Fast Image-to-Video - Animate an input image using Google's Veo 3.1 Fast model. Supports 720p/1080p resolution, 8 second duration, auto/16:9/9:16/1:1 aspect ratios, and optional audio generation. Input images up to 8MB via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐⭐

i2v-kamui-veo31.description: Google Veo3.1 Image-to-Video - Animate an input image using Google's Veo 3.1 model. Supports natural motion and realistic animations with prompt-guided animation control. Features 720p/1080p resolution, 8 second duration, auto/16:9/9:16/1:1 aspect ratios, and optional audio generation (33% less credits if disabled). Accepts images up to 8MB. Best for creating professional animated videos from static images via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

r2v-kamui-veo31.description: Google Veo3.1 Reference-to-Video - Generate videos from reference image(s) and text using Google's Veo 3.1 model. The prompt should describe how to animate between the first and last frame including action, style, camera motion, and ambiance. Supports 720p/1080p resolution, 8 second duration, 16:9 or 9:16 aspect ratio, and optional audio generation (33% less credits if disabled). Accepts images up to 8MB. Ideal for consistent subject animation across multiple frames via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

flf2v-kamui-veo31.description: Google Veo3.1 First-Last-Frame-to-Video - Generate videos by animating between a first and last frame using Google's Veo 3.1 model. The prompt should describe how to animate between the frames including action, style, camera motion, and ambiance. Supports 720p/1080p resolution, 8 second duration, auto/16:9/9:16/1:1 aspect ratios, and optional audio generation (33% less credits if disabled). Accepts images up to 8MB each. Best for creating smooth transitions between two specific frames via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

t2v-kamui-wan-25-preview.description: WAN 2.5 Preview Text-to-Video - Latest model with best visual quality and motion stability, supporting 480p/720p/1080p resolutions, multiple aspect ratios (16:9, 9:16, 1:1), 5 or 10-second video generation, and optional audio background music via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

i2v-kamui-ovi.description: OVI Image-to-Video - Generate video from an image with audio synthesis support. Features include text prompt-guided video generation, natural audio synthesis using special tags (<S>...<E> for speech, <AUDCAP>...<ENDAUDCAP> for audio description), and customizable inference steps via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

t2v-kamui-ovi.description: OVI Text-to-Video - Generate video from text prompts with audio synthesis support. Features include natural audio synthesis using special tags (<S>...<E> for speech, <AUDCAP>...<ENDAUDCAP> for audio description), multiple resolution options (512x992, 992x512, 960x512, 512x960, 720x720, 448x1120, 1120x448), and customizable inference steps via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

i2i3d-kamui-hyper3d-rodin-v2.description: Hyper3D Rodin V2 - Advanced 3D model generation from text prompts or images (up to 5), supporting multiple file formats (GLB, USDZ, FBX, OBJ, STL), various quality options, and PBR materials via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

t2i3d-kamui-meshy-v6-preview-text-to-3d.description: Meshy V6 Preview Text-to-3D - Latest high-quality 3D model generation from text descriptions. Supports two modes: 'preview' (untextured geometry, 20 credits) and 'full' (textured model, 30 credits). Features best-in-class text understanding, superior geometry/texture quality, multiple output formats (GLB, FBX, OBJ, USDZ), PBR materials, and customizable topology. Ideal for creative professionals requiring top-tier 3D assets via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

i2i3d-kamui-meshy-v6-preview-image-to-3d.description: Meshy V6 Preview Image-to-3D - High-quality 3D model generation from a single image. Latest Meshy-6 model with most accurate geometry reconstruction, superior texture quality, and processing time of 5-10 minutes. Supports multiple output formats (GLB, FBX, OBJ, USDZ), PBR materials (metallic, roughness, normal maps), customizable topology (quad/triangle), and advanced texturing options. Best for high-quality photo-to-3D conversion via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

i2i-kamui-qwen-image-edit-plus-lora.description: Qwen Image Edit Plus LoRA - Advanced multi-image editing with Qwen AI model and LoRA support. Features include editing multiple images (array), customizable size, LoRA weights (up to 3), safety checker, multiple output formats, and flexible inference steps via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

v2v-kamui-wan-vace-apps-long-reframe.description: WAN VACE Apps Long Reframe - Advanced video reframing that processes long videos scene-by-scene to adjust aspect ratio or composition. Supports multiple resolutions (240p-720p), aspect ratios (auto/16:9/1:1/9:16), frame interpolation models (rife/film), automatic scene detection, zoom control, and border trimming via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

t2v-kamui-openai-sora.description: OpenAI Sora - State-of-the-art video generation with text-to-video, image-to-video (first frame reference), and remix capabilities. Two models available: 'sora-2' (fast, flexible, good for iteration) and 'sora-2-pro' (production-grade quality). Supports multiple resolutions (720p, 1080p, portrait HD), customizable duration, and 24-hour download URLs for generated videos via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

misc-kamui-hunyuan-part.description: Hunyuan Part - 3D model segmentation tool. Process 3D models (.glb or .obj) to generate segmented meshes with point-based prompts. Returns segmented mesh, three mask meshes, best mask index, and IoU scores via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

i2i-kamui-lucidflux.description: Lucidflux - AI-powered image upscaling and restoration. Restore low-quality images into high-resolution, clean results using advanced diffusion model. Supports customizable target resolution (width/height), inference steps (1-100), guidance control, and seed-based reproducibility. Perfect for enhancing and restoring degraded images via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

i2i-kamui-image2pixel.description: Image2Pixel - Convert images into retro pixel art style with customizable color palette, pixel scale detection, downscaling methods, and advanced cleanup options via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

i2i3d-kamui-meshy-v5-multi-image-to-3d.description: Meshy-5 Multi-Image-to-3D - Convert 1-4 images of the same object into a single high-quality 3D model. Better geometry from multiple viewpoints, consistent lighting recommended. Supports topology (quad/triangle), target polycount, symmetry, remesh, PBR textures, and safety checker. Processing time: 3–7 minutes via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐

i2v-kamui-lynx.description: Lynx Image-to-Video - Animate a subject image into a short video using prompt guidance, with controls for resolution, aspect ratio, FPS, frames count, guidance scales, and identity preservation via Kamui Code ⭐⭐

i2v-kamui-pixverse-v5.description: Pixverse V5 Image-to-Video - Generate videos from a single image with prompt guidance. Supports aspect ratios (16:9, 4:3, 1:1, 3:4, 9:16), resolutions (360p–1080p), durations (5s/8s), negative prompts, styles (anime, 3d_animation, clay, comic, cyberpunk), and seed for reproducibility via Kamui Code ⭐⭐

i2v-kamui-pixverse-v5-transition.description: Pixverse V5 Transition - Create a smooth transition video between two images. Supports aspect ratios (16:9, 4:3, 1:1, 3:4, 9:16), resolutions (360p–1080p), durations (5s/8s), negative prompts, styles (anime, 3d_animation, clay, comic, cyberpunk), and seed via Kamui Code ⭐⭐

t2v-kamui-pixverse-v5.description: Pixverse V5 Text-to-Video - Generate videos from text prompts. Supports aspect ratios (16:9, 4:3, 1:1, 3:4, 9:16), resolutions (360p–1080p), durations (5s/8s), negative prompts, styles (anime, 3d_animation, clay, comic, cyberpunk), and seed for reproducibility via Kamui Code ⭐⭐

t2v-kamui-wan-alpha.description: WAN Alpha - Generate videos with transparency support from text prompts. Features include customizable resolution (240p–720p), aspect ratios (16:9, 1:1, 9:16), frame count (default: 81), FPS control (default: 16), sampler options (unipc, dpm++, euler), video quality settings (low, medium, high, maximum), multiple output formats (X264 .mp4, VP9 .webm, PRORES4444 .mov, GIF .gif), and advanced mask controls for transparency effects via Kamui Code ⭐⭐⭐
